      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, calpol IS paracetamol, right? so if i give him the calpol and then another paracetamol medicine it’s the same thing. if i give him 2.5ml of the calpol now and then another 2.5ml of a different paracetamol liquid in an hour, that should be fine to knock the fever out? i'm just desperate for him to stop crying.",
